- Search Advertising: Leveraging search engine platforms for advertising enables businesses to target users based on their search intent, increasing the relevance of ads.
- Location-Based Advertising: Location-based advertising utilizes geolocation data to deliver hyper-targeted ads based on the user's physical location, enhancing the effectiveness of campaigns.
- Messaging Advertising: Messaging advertising involves reaching users through messaging platforms, providing a direct and personalized way to communicate with the audience.
- Mobile Video Advertising: Mobile video ads are gaining popularity due to the widespread consumption of video content on mobile devices, offering a visually engaging way to convey brand messages.

